![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873156-7828.jpeg) ОкремийСтрілецький батальйон Києва завершує злагодження / Фото: КМВА  [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873156-7828.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873156-7828.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873156-4015.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873156-4015.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873156-9517.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873156-9517.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873156-3565.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873156-3565.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873156-3186.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873156-3186.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873156-7623.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873156-7623.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873157-3052.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873157-3052.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873157-3386.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873157-3386.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873157-7345.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873157-7345.jpeg) [![](Images/yкринформ/2023-04-07T16-20-16-03-00/630_360_1680873157-6542.jpeg)](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680873157-6542.jpeg)

