Images: ["[630_360_16808...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/thumb_files/630_360_1680879509-469.jpg)", "[1680879509-45...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680879509-459.jpg)", "[1680879509-22...](https://static.ukrinform.com/photos/2023_04/1680879509-224.jpg)"]

