Images: ['[photo_2023-04-07_14-00-22.jpg](https://armyinform.com.ua/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/photo_2023-04-07_14-00-22.jpg)', '[642ee1d07a750.jpg](https://vechirniy.kyiv.ua/uploads/2023/04/06/642ee1d07a750.jpg)', '[642edc813ffca.jpg](https://vechirniy.kyiv.ua/uploads/2023/04/06/642edc813ffca.jpg)']

